description: ResourcePartitions: Table describing resource partition configurations for each cell in a given area, including administrative controls and identifiers.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of data), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely an arbitrary identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), ResourcePartitions.zzzTemporary* (unused temporary columns), ResourcePartitions.rrpAdmCtrlRejPaReqOvlGbr (boolean indicating overlap request rejection control), ResourcePartitions.gbrAdmCtrlPerPartition (boolean indicating per-partition administrative control), ResourcePartitions.gbrPartitioning (boolean indicating if partitioning is enabled), ResourcePartitions.resourcePartitionsId (unique resource partition ID).
